      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ رَجُلٍ نَسِيَ أَنْ يَطُوفُ بَيْنَ اَلصَّفَا وَ اَلْمَرْوَةِ قَالَ «يُطَافُ عَنْهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2848 - Al-‘Ala’ narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim, from one of the Imams (as):\n\"I asked him about a man who forgot to perform the Sa’i (the walking) between Safa and Marwah. Imam (as) said: 'It can be performed on his behalf.'\""
        ]
